node.text:
💫💥IT’S GIVE AWAY TIME💥💫
Please read ALL of the below!

This week we are giving away 2 sets of these adorable matching Parent, Child cat socks by @coucousuzette 🐈‍⬛ 🧦 ❤️

🚨TO ENTER🚨
• FOLLOW @coucousuzette 
• FOLLOW @designdunkerdude 
• LIKE this post
• TAG 2 friends 

Winner will be selected at random on Saturday 18th September! Good Luck everybody! ❤️

NOTE: The winner will be contacted by direct message from THIS account. You will NOT need to click any links or provide any credit card information.

#socks #sock #socksfetish #socksofinstagram #sockdesign #newsocks #matching #matchingsocks #designdunker #textiledesign #fabricdesign #fabrics #cats #catdesign #catsofinstagram #catsocks #felinefriends #mamanddaughter #dadanddaughter #productdesigner #comp #giveaways #designmilk #designboom #dezeen #diseño
